@startuml Sequence_Performance

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "API" as API
participant "Redis Cache" as Cache
participant "Database" as DB

== Cached Request ==
User -> Client: Request data
Client -> API: GET /api/data
API -> Cache: Check cache

alt Data in cache
    Cache --> API: Cached data
    API --> Client: Return cached data
    Client --> User: Display (fast)
else Data not in cache
    Cache --> API: Cache miss
    API -> DB: Query database
    DB --> API: Data
    API -> Cache: Store in cache
    API --> Client: Return data
    Client --> User: Display
end

== Lazy Loading ==
User -> Client: Scroll page
Client -> Client: Detect viewport
Client -> Client: Load visible components
Client -> Client: Lazy load images
Client -> Client: Load on demand
Client --> User: Progressive rendering

== Code Splitting ==
Client -> Client: Load route
Client -> Client: Split bundle
Client -> Client: Load route chunk
Client -> Client: Initialize route
Client --> User: Render route

@enduml

